<title type="html"><![CDATA[Reciting The Qur`an In A Loud Tone Inside The Masjid]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=955&amp;p=999#p999"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Question:</span></strong> He was asked regarding reciting the Qur`an in a loud tone inside the Masjid?<br /><br /><span style="color: #0000FF"><strong>Response:</strong></span> He replied: that such an act is considered Makruh [reprehensible] if there is somebody inside [present in] the Masjid, praying Salaah, because that person will get distracted by the loud recitation.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Reference:</span></strong>  Fataawaa Ibn Abee Zayd al-Qayruwaanee, Fataawaa regarding the Salaah – Fatwa No.66 Page 120<br /><br /><em>Footnotes</em><br /><br />[1] Makruh: Literally meaning abominable or reprehensible. According to the Scholars of Islamic Jurisprudence, it can be defined in the following words: Refraining from doing an act out of obedience to Allaah [based upon proof and evidence], which would subsequently necessitate a reward. However, the perpetrator is not eligible for punishment if the act is committed. For example, drinking whilst standing. [TN]<br /><br />[2] He is Abu Muhammad Abdullaah ibn Abee Zayd Abdur–Rahmaan Annafzee al-Qayruwaanee, nicknamed Maalik-Assageer [Little Maalik] for his in-depth knowledge of Imaam Maalik Ibn Anas`s opinions on the subsidiary issues of the Sharee`ah [Fiqh]. He was born in the year 310 AH corresponding to 922 CE in the north of Tunisia; he studied with the major scholars of his time and the number of his teachers exceeded to over 50. He authored over 38 books. One of his famous books is Muqaddamatul-Qayruwaanee, which is an explanation of the Salafee Aqeedah. This has been explained in detail by Allaamah Abdul-Muhsin al-Abbaad, the Muhaddith of Madeenah in the Prophet`s Masjid, may Allaah`s praise and peace be with him. Ibn Abee Zayd al-Qayruwaanee died in the year 386 A.H. on Monday evening in the month of Sha`baan at the age of 76. [TN]<br /><br />______________________________________________<br /><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><br />حكم عن الجهر بقراءة القرآن في المسجد<br /><br />المرجع: فتاوى ابن أبي زيد القيرواني، من فتاوى الصلاة، الرقم: 66، ص:120<br /><br />السؤال: و سئل الشيخ أبو محمّد ابن أبي زيد القيرواني عن الجهر بقراءة القرآن في المسجد؟<br /><br />الجواب: قال: يكره ذلك إذا كان فيه من يصلّي لأنّ ذلك يشغله<br /></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Wed Jan 04, 2017 11:09 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
